(1, 1, 10, 46, 20, 'Fresh Organic Broccoli – Nutritious, Crisp & Fresh Green', '2627639', 2, '87', '67359b8822084.png', 'Fresh, organic broccoli, packed with vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants. Ideal for steaming, roasting, or adding to salads and stir-fries, broccoli is a nutritious green vegetable that supports overall health and well-being.', '<p><strong>Fresh Organic Broccoli</strong> is a nutrient powerhouse that’s perfect for adding flavor, crunch, and color to your meals. With its rich green florets and hearty texture, broccoli is an essential vegetable in many dishes, from healthy salads to soups and stir-fries.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Fresh Organic Broccoli?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Packed with Nutrients:</strong> Broccoli is an excellent source of vitamin C, vitamin K, fiber, and folate. It also contains important minerals like potassium, calcium, and iron. The combination of these nutrients supports immune function, bone health, heart health, and overall vitality.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Antioxidant-Rich:</strong> Full of antioxidants, including sulforaphane and beta-carotene, broccoli helps to protect the body from oxidative stress and supports healthy aging. These antioxidants are essential for maintaining a strong immune system and fighting off inflammation.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Versatile &amp; Delicious:</strong> Whether you steam it, roast it with garlic and olive oil, add it to your stir-fries, or toss it into a fresh salad, broccoli is incredibly versatile. It’s also delicious when added to pasta dishes, casseroles, and even smoothies.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Supports a Healthy Lifestyle:</strong> Known for its cancer-fighting properties, broccoli is an excellent vegetable to include in a health-conscious diet. The high fiber content promotes digestive health, while its low calorie count makes it ideal for weight management.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Organic &amp; Fresh:</strong> Our broccoli is grown without pesticides or synthetic chemicals, ensuring a cleaner, healthier product for you and your family. Hand-harvested at its peak freshness, each bunch delivers the full range of benefits, both in taste and nutrition.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Add <strong>Fresh Organic Broccoli</strong> to your cart today and enjoy a nutritious, versatile, and delicious vegetable that will elevate your meals and support your health. Whether you’re looking to improve your diet or simply want a tasty addition to your plate, this broccoli will not disappoint.</p>\r\n<h4> </h4>', '3.14', '0.00', NULL, '2024-11-16 05:03:58', NULL),
(2, 2, 10, 46, 19, 'Fresh Crisp Lettuce – Organic, Nutrient-Packed & Refreshing Green', '8916711', 2, '87', '67359d8c5e812.png', 'Fresh lettuce is a crisp and refreshing green that’s perfect for salads, sandwiches, wraps, and more. This organic variety is packed with vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants, making it a healthy and delicious choice for any meal. Enjoy the cool crunch and versatility of lettuce in all your favorite dishes.', '<p>Add a refreshing crunch to your meals with our <strong>Fresh Organic Lettuce</strong>. Known for its light, crisp texture and mild flavor, lettuce is an essential green that’s both versatile and healthy. Whether you\'re building a salad, layering it into a sandwich, or using it as a wrap for your favorite fillings, lettuce brings a crisp, hydrating element to any dish.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Fresh Lettuce?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Loaded with Nutrients:</strong> Lettuce is low in calories but rich in essential nutrients. It\'s an excellent source of vitamin K, which supports bone health, and vitamin A, which is important for eye health and immune function. Lettuce also contains folate, fiber, and a variety of minerals that promote overall well-being.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Hydrating and Refreshing:</strong> Lettuce is made up of over 90% water, making it one of the most hydrating vegetables available. It’s the perfect addition to summer salads, refreshing smoothies, or as a base for your healthy wraps and bowls.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Versatile in the Kitchen:</strong> Whether you\'re tossing it into a fresh garden salad, using it as a crunchy topping for tacos, or wrapping it around grilled chicken for a healthy meal, lettuce is a versatile green that works with almost any dish. It adds both texture and a mild flavor that pairs well with a variety of ingredients.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Supports a Healthy Lifestyle:</strong> With its high water content, lettuce helps with digestion and promotes hydration, which is essential for maintaining healthy skin, regulating body temperature, and supporting overall health. It’s also low in calories, making it a great choice for anyone looking to maintain or lose weight.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Organic and Fresh:</strong> Grown without pesticides or harmful chemicals, our lettuce is harvested fresh from organic farms, ensuring you get the cleanest, most nutritious product available.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Add a head of <strong>Fresh Organic Lettuce</strong> to your cart today and enjoy its crisp, refreshing flavor and health benefits in every bite. Whether you\'re preparing a light salad or creating a filling meal, this lettuce will be the perfect addition.</p>\r\n<h4> </h4>', '1.28', NULL, NULL, '2024-11-16 05:34:55', NULL),
(3, 2, 10, 46, 16, 'Premium Black Pepper – Bold, Spicy, and Essential for Every Kitchen', '7707135', 1, '83', '673480ee99fee.png', 'Add a kick to your meals with our Premium Black Pepper. Known for its bold, spicy flavor, this essential spice is perfect for seasoning all types of dishes—from meats and vegetables to soups and sauces. Bring depth and heat to your cooking with the finest black pepper available.', '<p>Our <strong>Premium Black Pepper</strong> is sourced from the best peppercorns and ground to perfection, ensuring a fresh, pungent spice that enhances the flavor of any dish. Whether you\'re cooking a savory steak, seasoning a salad, or adding zest to your soup, black pepper is a must-have for every kitchen.</p>\r\n<p>This versatile spice is perfect for daily use and adds a natural, aromatic heat to your dishes. It’s great for seasoning meats, vegetables, soups, marinades, or even sprinkles on salads for an extra burst of flavor. Packed with essential oils, <strong>black pepper</strong> not only adds heat but also aids in digestion, making it a healthy and flavorful addition to your meals.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Black Pepper?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Bold &amp; Spicy:</strong> Made from the finest black peppercorns for a strong, authentic flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile &amp; Convenient:</strong> Perfect for a wide range of dishes from meats to soups, sauces, and marinades.</li>\r\n<li><strong>No Artificial Additives:</strong> Made with no preservatives, fillers, or artificial colors—just pure, natural pepper.</li>\r\n<li><strong>A Healthy Choice:</strong> Rich in antioxidants, it enhances flavor and promotes digestion.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Easy to Use:</strong> Freshly ground to ensure maximum flavor and aroma every time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>High-Quality Peppercorns:</strong> Sourced from the best black peppercorns for rich, authentic flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile:</strong> Ideal for seasoning a wide range of dishes, from savory meats to vegetables, soups, and sauces.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Natural &amp; Pure:</strong> Free from preservatives and artificial additives.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Aromatic Heat:</strong> Adds a perfect balance of heat and flavor to your meals.</li>\r\n</ul>', '3.69', '0.00', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":2,\"name\":\"100g Pack\",\"price\":2,\"stock\":70},\"Quality\":{\"option_id\":6,\"name\":\"Organic Quality\",\"price\":2,\"stock\":70}}', '2024-11-16 05:34:55', NULL),
(4, 3, 10, 46, 3, 'Tender, Fresh, and Flavorful Cuts Mutton', '4253702', 1, '77', '6734540e9b35c.png', 'Our premium mutton meat is carefully selected from high-quality sources, offering tender, juicy cuts ideal for slow-cooking, grilling, or stewing. Whether you\'re preparing traditional mutton dishes or exploring new recipes, our mutton meat ensures rich, savory flavors in every bite.', '<p><strong>Premium Mutton Meat</strong> is sourced from carefully raised sheep, known for their rich flavor and exceptional tenderness. This high-quality mutton is perfect for a variety of cooking methods, from slow-roasting to grilling or simmering in flavorful stews. Whether you\'re preparing classic <strong>mutton curry</strong>, a hearty stew, or a grilled mutton chop, each cut delivers juicy, tender meat that is packed with deep, savory flavors.</p>\r\n<p>Our mutton is ethically sourced from trusted farms that prioritize animal welfare and sustainable farming practices. We ensure that each piece of mutton is handled with care, preserving its natural juices and tenderness for a delightful eating experience.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Mutton Meat?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Tender &amp; Flavorful:</strong> Each cut of mutton is guaranteed to be tender, juicy, and full of rich flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile Cuts:</strong> Available in a variety of cuts such as chops, stew meat, and leg of mutton, perfect for grilling, slow-cooking, or braising.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Ethically Sourced:</strong> Raised on trusted farms with a focus on humane farming practices and sustainability.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fresh &amp; Premium Quality:</strong> Our mutton is always fresh and carefully butchered to ensure the best possible taste and texture.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Ideal for Special Occasions:</strong> Whether you\'re preparing a family feast or a celebratory meal, our mutton meat is the perfect choice for an unforgettable dining experience.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Available Cuts:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Mutton Chops</strong> - Perfect for grilling, known for their rich, flavorful taste.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Leg of Mutton</strong> - Ideal for roasting, delivering tender and juicy meat.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Mutton Stew Meat</strong> - Perfect for slow-cooking, bringing out deep flavors in hearty stews.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Mutton Ribs</strong> - Great for grilling or braising, offering a delicious, savory flavor.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Fresh &amp; High-Quality:</strong> Sourced from responsible farms to ensure top-quality cuts.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Juicy &amp; Tender:</strong> Each cut is guaranteed to be tender, juicy, and flavorful.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Sustainably Raised:</strong> Our mutton is raised using environmentally responsible methods.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile &amp; Convenient:</strong> Ideal for slow cooking, grilling, or braising, perfect for various dishes.</li>\r\n</ul>', '14.90', '18.90', NULL, '2024-11-16 05:53:46', NULL),
(5, 3, 10, 46, 7, 'Fresh, Sweet Mangoes – Tropical, Juicy, and Irresistible', '3946823', 1, '79', '67346c535ff36.png', 'Our fresh mangoes are a tropical paradise in every bite. With their juicy, sweet flesh and rich flavor, they are perfect for snacking, adding to smoothies, or topping off your favorite desserts. Enjoy the taste of sunshine with every mango!', '<p>Indulge in the ultimate tropical treat with our <strong>fresh, ripe mangoes</strong>—sourced from the best farms and handpicked at the peak of ripeness to ensure a rich, sweet flavor and a juicy, tender texture. Mangoes are known for their vibrant orange flesh, aromatic fragrance, and deliciously smooth taste.</p>\r\n<p>Packed with <strong>vitamins</strong> and <strong>antioxidants</strong>, mangoes are not only a delicious treat but also a nutritious addition to your diet. They are rich in <strong>vitamin C</strong>, which supports your immune system and promotes healthy skin. Whether eaten fresh, blended into smoothies, or added to salsas and desserts, these mangoes will elevate any dish with their tropical sweetness.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Mangoes?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Naturally Sweet &amp; Juicy:</strong> Each mango is bursting with natural sweetness and flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Rich in Vitamin C:</strong> A great source of vitamin C to support your immune system and enhance skin health.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile:</strong> Perfect for snacking, smoothies, fruit salads, salsas, or as a topping for desserts.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fresh &amp; Ripe:</strong> Handpicked at the peak of ripeness to ensure maximum sweetness and juiciness.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Nutritious:</strong> Packed with vitamins, antioxidants, and fiber for a healthy and energy-boosting snack.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Juicy &amp; Sweet:</strong> Our mangoes are selected for their perfect balance of sweetness and juiciness.</li>\r\n<li><strong>High in Vitamin C:</strong> Great for boosting your immune system and skin health.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile:</strong> Enjoy them fresh, as a smoothie ingredient, in fruit salads, or on top of desserts.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Freshly Sourced:</strong> Handpicked from the best orchards to ensure premium quality and flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Healthy:</strong> Loaded with essential nutrients like fiber, antioxidants, and vitamins to support overall well-being.</li>\r\n</ul>', '3.71', '0.00', NULL, '2024-11-16 05:53:46', NULL),
(6, 4, 10, 46, 5, 'Fresh, Juicy Oranges – Sweet & Refreshing Citrus Fruit', '5442882', 3, '79', '673468eedf5da.png', 'Our fresh oranges are packed with natural sweetness and refreshing citrus flavor. Perfect for juicing, snacking, or adding to your favorite dishes, these juicy, sun-ripened oranges are the perfect way to boost your day with vitamin C and delicious taste.', '<p>Our <strong>fresh oranges</strong> are sourced from the best orchards, carefully harvested to ensure they are at their peak ripeness. These <strong>sweet and juicy oranges</strong> are packed with <strong>vitamin C</strong>, fiber, and antioxidants, making them a healthy addition to any diet.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you enjoy them fresh, as juice, or incorporated into smoothies, salads, or baked goods, our oranges are always bursting with flavor. Each orange is hand-picked to ensure only the finest quality, offering a balance of sweetness and tanginess that makes them irresistible.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Fresh Oranges?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Sweet &amp; Juicy:</strong> Each orange is full of natural sweetness and citrusy tang.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Rich in Vitamin C:</strong> A great source of vitamin C to boost your immune system.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile:</strong> Perfect for snacking, juicing, smoothies, or as a topping for salads and desserts.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Sun-Ripened:</strong> Grown in optimal conditions, ensuring they are juicy, tender, and full of flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Ethically Grown:</strong> Sourced from responsible orchards that prioritize sustainability and ethical farming practices.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Fresh &amp; Natural:</strong> Our oranges are picked at the peak of ripeness to guarantee the best taste and quality.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Healthy &amp; Nutritious:</strong> Rich in vitamins, antioxidants, and fiber to support a healthy lifestyle.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Delicious &amp; Versatile:</strong> Ideal for a variety of uses – from fresh snacking to juicing and more.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Sustainably Sourced:</strong> Grown with care in eco-friendly orchards.</li>\r\n</ul>', '2.32', '3.90', NULL, '2024-11-16 05:55:54', NULL),
(7, 5, 10, 46, 1, 'Premium Beef Meat - Fresh and Tender', '5957299', 1, '77', '673442cadfd33.png', 'Discover premium beef meat, carefully sourced for its tenderness and rich flavor. Perfect for grilling, stews, steaks, and more. Our beef cuts are hand-selected to ensure top quality for all your culinary needs.', '<p><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\">Our <strong>Premium Beef Meat</strong> is sourced from the finest farms, ensuring each cut is of the highest quality. With a focus on <strong>freshness</strong>, <strong>tenderness</strong>, and <strong>flavor</strong>, our beef is perfect for a wide variety of cooking styles. From grilling mouthwatering steaks to simmering rich stews or slow-roasting a delicious roast, our beef ensures a satisfying and flavorful meal every time.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\">Each piece of beef is carefully butchered and packed to preserve its natural juices, ensuring maximum tenderness and flavor in every bite. Our premium cuts include tenderloin, rib-eye, sirloin, and more—each cut designed to provide you with the ideal cooking experience.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\">Whether you\'re a professional chef or an amateur home cook, our beef will meet your highest expectations. It’s perfect for <strong>grilling</strong>, <strong>pan-frying</strong>, <strong>braising</strong>, or making <strong>hearty soups and stews</strong>.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Key Features:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Fresh &amp; High-Quality:</strong> Sourced from trusted farms for the freshest cuts.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Tender &amp; Flavorful:</strong> Each cut is guaranteed to be tender, juicy, and full of rich flavor.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Versatile Cuts:</strong> Available in a variety of cuts to suit your cooking needs—steaks, roasts, stews, and more.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Ideal for Any Occasion:</strong> Perfect for everything from casual family meals to special occasions and barbecues.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Why Choose Our Beef?</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Sustainably Sourced:</strong> Our beef comes from responsibly managed farms that focus on animal welfare and environmental sustainability.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Carefully Packaged:</strong> Our beef is vacuum-sealed to maintain freshness and flavor, ensuring that it reaches you in perfect condition.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Ethically Raised:</strong> Our cattle are raised without hormones or unnecessary antibiotics, guaranteeing natural and healthy meat.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Available Cuts:</strong></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Ribeye Steaks</strong> - Perfect for grilling, known for its marbling and flavor.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Sirloin Steaks</strong> - A lean, flavorful cut perfect for pan-searing or grilling.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Tenderloin</strong> - The most tender cut, ideal for special occasions.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"color:rgb(0,0,0);\"><strong>Beef Stew Meat</strong> - Ideal for slow cooking and making rich, comforting stews.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '10.00', '12.00', NULL, '2024-11-16 06:14:20', NULL),
(8, 5, 10, 46, 4, 'Succulent Duck Meat – Rich, Tender, and Full of Flavor', '8585452', 1, '77', '6734570d81afd.png', 'Our premium duck meat offers a unique and rich flavor, sourced from healthy ducks raised in the best conditions. Perfect for roasting, grilling, or slow-cooking, this tender meat is sure to enhance any dish, from a festive dinner to a weeknight meal.', '<p>Experience the rich and savory taste of <strong>Premium Duck Meat</strong>, carefully selected for its tenderness, flavor, and quality. Our duck meat is sourced from healthy, ethically raised ducks and is perfect for a variety of cooking methods, including roasting, grilling, and braising.</p>\r\n<p>The unique, succulent flavor of duck meat sets it apart from other poultry, and our premium cuts ensure a tender, juicy bite every time. Whether you\'re preparing a <strong>classic duck breast</strong>, a flavorful <strong>duck leg</strong>, or a whole <strong>roast duck</strong>, each cut is crafted to deliver the deep, rich taste that makes duck such a sought-after delicacy.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Duck Meat?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Tender &amp; Flavorful:</strong> Each cut of duck is guaranteed to be juicy, tender, and bursting with rich flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile Cuts:</strong> Available in a variety of cuts such as duck breasts, legs, wings, and whole ducks, perfect for grilling, roasting, or slow cooking.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Ethically Sourced:</strong> Raised in humane, sustainable farming environments, our ducks are treated with care to ensure the best quality meat.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Premium Quality:</strong> Our duck meat is processed and handled with care to maintain freshness and tenderness.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Ideal for Special Occasions:</strong> Whether it’s for a family dinner or a celebratory feast, duck meat adds elegance and flavor to any meal.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Available Cuts:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Duck Breast:</strong> Ideal for pan-searing, grilling, or roasting. Rich, tender, and juicy.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Duck Legs:</strong> Perfect for slow-cooking or roasting, delivering a melt-in-your-mouth experience.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Duck Wings:</strong> Great for grilling, frying, or making rich broths.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Whole Duck:</strong> Perfect for roasting or braising, ideal for festive occasions or family meals.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Rich &amp; Tender:</strong> Guaranteed fresh, tender, and flavorful cuts with every piece.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Free-Range Ducks:</strong> Sourced from ethical, free-range farms ensuring the best care for the ducks.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile &amp; Delicious:</strong> Ideal for multiple cooking methods—roasting, grilling, or slow cooking.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Ethically Raised:</strong> Our ducks are raised in healthy, humane conditions with sustainable farming practices.</li>\r\n</ul>', '19.90', '24.90', NULL, '2024-11-16 06:14:20', NULL),
(9, 6, 11, 47, 43, 'Contemporary Counter Stools (Set of 2)', '2955783', 1, '101', '673c2e7261b1d.png', 'Add versatility to your dining space with the Contemporary Counter Stools, featuring a modern design and compact build. These stools are perfect for kitchen counters, dining tables, or casual bar setups.', '<p>The <strong>Contemporary Counter Stools</strong> offer a perfect combination of style and functionality. With their sleek metal frames and cushioned seats, these stools provide sturdy support and unmatched comfort. The ergonomic design ensures optimal seating posture, while the footrest adds extra convenience.</p>\r\n<p>Designed to fit seamlessly under counters or tall dining tables, these stools maximize space while providing a contemporary aesthetic. The easy-to-clean faux leather upholstery ensures they stay looking fresh even in busy households.</p>\r\n<p>Perfect for casual meals or entertaining guests, the <strong>Contemporary Counter Stools</strong> are a versatile and stylish addition to any dining area.</p>', '199.99', '259.99', NULL, '2024-11-19 08:35:12', NULL),
(10, 6, 11, 47, 42, 'Expandable Dining Table', '1668617', 1, '101', '673c2e2acf8a3.png', 'The Expandable Dining Table is designed to adapt to your dining needs with its adjustable size. Perfect for intimate family dinners or large gatherings, this table is a centerpiece of functionality and elegance.', '<p>The <strong>Expandable Dining Table</strong> brings versatility and sophistication to your dining area. Featuring a durable hardwood construction with a smooth, polished finish, this table is built to withstand daily use while maintaining its elegant appearance.</p>\r\n<p>The innovative extendable design allows you to adjust the table length effortlessly, accommodating both small and large gatherings. Its sturdy legs provide excellent stability, and the scratch-resistant surface ensures easy maintenance.</p>\r\n<p>With its timeless design and neutral tones, the <strong>Expandable Dining Table</strong> complements a wide range of dining room styles. Whether hosting a dinner party or enjoying a family meal, this table adapts to your needs with elegance and ease.</p>', '999.99', '1199.99', '{\"Size Options\":{\"option_id\":46,\"name\":\"Compact (Seats 4, expands to 6)\",\"price\":89.99,\"stock\":100},\"Material\":{\"option_id\":49,\"name\":\"Engineered Wood\",\"price\":94.99,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-19 08:35:12', NULL),
(11, 7, 11, 47, 41, 'Elegant Dining Chair Set (Set of 2)', '2319423', 1, '101', '673c2ddce7c5d.png', 'Upgrade your dining area with the Elegant Dining Chair Set, featuring a timeless design and superior comfort. Perfect for both casual meals and formal gatherings, these chairs combine elegance and durability.', '<p>The <strong>Elegant Dining Chair Set</strong> is designed to enhance your dining experience with its stylish design and exceptional comfort. Crafted with a solid wood frame, these chairs ensure long-lasting durability and support. The cushioned seats are upholstered in soft, stain-resistant fabric, making them both comfortable and easy to maintain.</p>\r\n<p>With their ergonomic backrests and sturdy construction, these chairs provide excellent posture support for long dinners or entertaining guests. The neutral-toned upholstery and sleek design allow them to seamlessly blend into any dining room decor.</p>\r\n<p>Perfect as a standalone piece or paired with a dining table, the <strong>Elegant Dining Chair Set</strong> brings sophistication and practicality to your home.</p>', '117.50', '299.99', '{\"Color Family\":{\"option_id\":33,\"name\":\"Grey\",\"price\":50,\"stock\":100},\"Size\":{\"option_id\":37,\"name\":\"Small\",\"price\":0,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-19 08:37:10', NULL),
(12, 8, 11, 47, 38, 'Premium Modular Kitchen Cabinets', '8243583', 1, '109', '673b257a4952e.png', 'Transform your kitchen with the Premium Modular Kitchen Cabinets, featuring a modern design, ample storage space, and durable construction. Perfect for organizing cookware, utensils, and pantry items, these cabinets blend style and practicality to elevate your kitchen.', '<p>The <strong>Premium Modular Kitchen Cabinets</strong> are the ultimate storage solution for a modern, functional kitchen. Designed with sleek lines and a contemporary aesthetic, these cabinets bring a sophisticated touch to any home while keeping your cooking essentials neatly organized and easily accessible.</p>\r\n<p>Crafted from high-quality engineered wood and finished with a durable laminate coating, these cabinets are built to withstand daily use. The scratch-resistant and easy-to-clean surface ensures that they maintain their pristine appearance even in the busiest kitchens. Each unit is equipped with soft-close hinges to prevent slamming and ensure smooth, silent operation.</p>\r\n<p>The modular design of the <strong>Premium Modular Kitchen Cabinets</strong> allows you to customize your kitchen layout to suit your needs. With a combination of spacious drawers, adjustable shelves, and closed compartments, you can effortlessly organize everything from pots and pans to spices and pantry goods. The included pull-out tray and corner storage solutions maximize efficiency and make the most of your kitchen space.</p>', '1499.99', '1699.99', '{\"Finish\":{\"option_id\":59,\"name\":\"Semi-Gloss\",\"price\":210,\"stock\":100},\"Material\":{\"option_id\":63,\"name\":\"Plywood with Veneer Finish\",\"price\":290,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-19 08:39:20', NULL),
(13, 9, 11, 47, 40, 'Classic Six-Drawer Dresser', '8025256', 1, '99', '673c2cec70d19.png', 'Organize your bedroom with the Classic Six-Drawer Dresser, a timeless piece offering ample storage and a stylish design. Perfect for clothing, linens, or personal items, this dresser is both functional and elegant.', '<p>The <strong>Classic Six-Drawer Dresser</strong> is the ideal blend of sophistication and practicality, designed to complement any bedroom decor. With its sleek lines and spacious design, this dresser provides generous storage space to keep your room neat and organized.</p>\r\n<p>Constructed from high-quality engineered wood and finished with a durable laminate coating, this dresser is built to last. Its six roomy drawers glide smoothly on metal runners, making it easy to access your belongings. Each drawer is fitted with sleek, contemporary hardware for added style and convenience.</p>\r\n<p>The dresser’s classic design and versatile finish allow it to seamlessly fit into both traditional and modern interiors. Whether you use it to store clothing, linens, or accessories, its sturdy build ensures it will serve your needs for years to come.</p>', '499.99', '699.99', '{\"Material\":{\"option_id\":38,\"name\":\"Engineered Wood\",\"price\":89,\"stock\":100},\"Finish\":{\"option_id\":41,\"name\":\"Glossy\",\"price\":70,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-20 04:54:51', NULL),
(14, 10, 11, 47, 36, 'Modern Comfort Kitchen Table', '6863478', 1, '109', '673b234862625.png', 'The Modern Comfort Kitchen Table combines style and practicality, making it a perfect seating solution for your dining area. With its ergonomic design and durable materials, this chair offers unmatched comfort and elegance for everyday use.', '<p>Elevate your kitchen or dining area with the <strong>Modern Comfort Kitchen Table </strong>, a versatile and stylish seating option designed for modern homes. Built with a sturdy frame and ergonomic design, this chair provides exceptional support and comfort during meals, family gatherings, or casual kitchen chats.</p>\r\n<p>Crafted from high-quality wood and reinforced with metal accents, the chair is both durable and visually appealing. Its cushioned seat and contoured backrest are upholstered in a water-resistant fabric, making it easy to clean and ideal for busy households. The non-slip feet ensure stability while protecting your floors from scratches.</p>', '51.99', '120.99', '{\"Finish\":{\"option_id\":68,\"name\":\"Matte\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100},\"Material\":{\"option_id\":71,\"name\":\"Plywood with Veneer Finish\",\"price\":20,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-20 05:41:16', NULL),
(15, 11, 11, 47, 33, 'Elegant 5-Drawer Chest of Drawers', '8272992', 1, '111', '673b07fdf24ba.png', 'The Elegant 5-Drawer Chest of Drawers is a stylish and practical storage solution that brings both organization and sophistication to any bedroom or living space. With five spacious drawers, this chest offers ample storage for clothes, accessories, and personal items while enhancing your room’s decor.', '<p>The <strong>Elegant 5-Drawer Chest of Drawers</strong> is designed to provide efficient storage while adding a touch of modern elegance to your home. With its sleek, contemporary design, this chest fits seamlessly into any bedroom, guest room, or living area, offering a perfect balance of form and function.</p>\r\n<p>Crafted from high-quality wood and finished with a smooth, durable surface, the chest provides long-lasting durability. The five spacious drawers glide smoothly, offering ample storage space for clothes, linens, toys, or any other household items. Each drawer is designed to hold a substantial amount of weight, ensuring that you can store your essentials without worry.</p>', '249.99', '299.99', '{\"Material\":{\"option_id\":64,\"name\":\"Engineered Wood\",\"price\":20,\"stock\":100},\"Size Options\":{\"option_id\":67,\"name\":\"Large\",\"price\":50,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-20 09:38:35', NULL),
(16, 11, 11, 47, 39, 'Spacious Double-Door Wardrobe with Shelves', '1311135', 1, '111', '673b27ab7549f.png', 'Keep your belongings organized and your bedroom clutter-free with the Spacious Double-Door Wardrobe with Shelves. This elegant storage solution features ample space for clothing, accessories, and more, combining practicality with modern style.', '<p>The <strong>Spacious Double-Door Wardrobe with Shelves</strong> is designed to meet all your storage needs while enhancing your bedroom\'s decor. With a thoughtfully planned interior, this wardrobe provides a mix of hanging space, adjustable shelves, and drawers to accommodate clothing, shoes, and accessories effortlessly.</p>\r\n<p>Crafted from premium engineered wood with a scratch-resistant finish, this wardrobe is built to last. The double doors open to reveal a spacious interior that is both functional and visually appealing. Adjustable shelves allow you to customize the space to fit larger or smaller items, while the sturdy hanging rod keeps your clothes wrinkle-free and organized.</p>', '799.99', '999.99', '{\"Material\":{\"option_id\":54,\"name\":\"Engineered Wood\",\"price\":90,\"stock\":100},\"Size Options\":{\"option_id\":57,\"name\":\"Large\",\"price\":180,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-20 09:38:35', NULL),
(17, 11, 11, 47, 30, 'Ergonomic Executive Office Desk', '8371746', 1, '107', '673b04c186281.png', 'Upgrade your workspace with the Ergonomic Executive Office Desk, designed for comfort, productivity, and modern style. Featuring a spacious work surface, ample storage, and a sleek design, this desk is perfect for any professional setting.', '<p>The <strong>Ergonomic Executive Office Desk</strong> is built to provide both function and style, making it an ideal choice for your home office or corporate workspace. Designed with the modern professional in mind, this desk offers a generous work surface, allowing you to spread out your computer, documents, and other essentials comfortably. Whether you\'re managing your business, working remotely, or handling everyday tasks, this desk is made to support your productivity and comfort.</p>\r\n<p>Crafted from high-quality wood and durable metal components, the desk offers both strength and longevity. The smooth, laminated surface provides a sleek look while being easy to maintain. The ergonomic design promotes better posture by offering a spacious, organized layout that reduces clutter and encourages a clean, efficient workspace.</p>', '399.99', '459.99', '{\"Features\":{\"option_id\":78,\"name\":\"Cable Management Grommets\",\"price\":40,\"stock\":100},\"Color Options\":{\"option_id\":81,\"name\":\"Grey Maple\",\"price\":80,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-20 09:38:35', NULL),
(18, 12, 12, 48, 70, 'Adidas Ultraboost 22 Performance Gym Shoes', '6864024', 1, '119', '674165256c2a1.png', 'The Adidas Ultraboost 22 Performance Gym Shoes are engineered for maximum comfort and performance, featuring a responsive Boost midsole and breathable mesh upper. Perfect for both gym workouts and outdoor activities, these shoes provide the support and flexibility you need to stay at the top of your game.', '<p>The <strong>Adidas Ultraboost 22 Performance Gym Shoes</strong> are designed to help you perform at your best, no matter the workout. The signature Boost midsole technology offers superior cushioning and energy return with every step, providing a responsive feel that helps you power through intense sessions. The breathable mesh upper enhances airflow, keeping your feet cool and dry during even the toughest workouts.</p>\r\n<p>These shoes feature a durable rubber outsole with a grippy pattern, providing excellent traction on a variety of surfaces. Whether you\'re lifting, running, or doing agility drills, the <strong>Ultraboost 22</strong> ensures stability and support, giving you the confidence to push yourself further. The sleek, modern design with reflective details also adds a stylish touch, making these shoes perfect for both the gym and casual wear.</p>\r\n<p>Available in a range of colors, the <strong>Adidas Ultraboost 22 Gym Shoes</strong> combine performance with comfort and style, making them an essential addition to any fitness enthusiast\'s collection.</p>', '148.99', '259.99', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":120,\"name\":\"23.5 cm\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":125,\"name\":\"Red\",\"price\":15,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-24 05:45:36', NULL),
(19, 13, 12, 48, 68, 'Nike Essential Men\'s Training Shorts for Optimal Performance and Comfort', '5706987', 1, '119', '6741629d89ced.png', 'The Nike Men\'s Training Shorts are designed for ultimate comfort and flexibility during your workout. Made with lightweight, breathable fabric, these shorts provide freedom of movement and ensure you stay cool and dry throughout your training session.', '<p>The <strong>Nike Men\'s Training Shorts</strong> are built to support your active lifestyle, whether you\'re hitting the gym, going for a run, or engaging in intense sports activities. Crafted from high-quality, moisture-wicking fabric, these shorts help keep you dry and comfortable by drawing sweat away from your skin. The lightweight material allows for easy movement, ensuring you stay focused on your performance without restriction.</p>\r\n<p>Featuring an elastic waistband with an adjustable drawstring, the shorts provide a secure fit that can be customized for your comfort. The sleek design includes side pockets for convenient storage of essentials like keys or a phone. Perfect for any workout, the <strong>Nike Men\'s Training Shorts</strong> offer both functionality and style, making them a versatile addition to your fitness wardrobe. Available in various colors, they pair well with any training gear.</p>', '39.99', '49.99', '{\"Color\":{\"option_id\":126,\"name\":\"Black\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100},\"Length\":{\"option_id\":137,\"name\":\"Mid-Thigh\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-24 05:49:41', NULL),
(20, 14, 12, 48, 65, 'Bigmo Club Premium Performance Football Jersey for Ultimate Comfort and Durability', '4062739', 1, '119', '67417335714cf.png', 'The Bigmo Club Football Jersey is a tribute to the legendary club’s legacy, combining traditional design with modern performance features. Whether you\'re cheering from the stands or playing on the pitch, this jersey is perfect for any Barça supporter.', '<p>The Bigmo Club Football Jersey blends the club’s iconic blaugrana stripes with cutting-edge performance technology. Made from lightweight, breathable fabric, this jersey is designed to keep you cool and comfortable during intense activities or casual wear. Featuring the classic FC Barcelona crest on the chest, it represents the pride, passion, and success of one of football\'s greatest clubs.</p>\r\n<p>The jersey\'s advanced moisture-wicking technology ensures you stay dry and comfortable, while the breathable mesh panels enhance ventilation and airflow. With a sleek, modern fit, the Bigmo Club Football Jersey allows for freedom of movement, making it perfect for both athletic performance and everyday wear.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re wearing it to show your support at Camp Nou or on your next football match, this jersey is a must-have for all true Barça fans. Celebrate the pride of the Catalan club with the Bigmo Club Football Jersey, and wear your passion on your sleeve.</p>', '599.99', '899.99', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":138,\"name\":\"L\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":143,\"name\":\"Red\",\"price\":20,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-24 05:53:53', NULL),
(21, 15, 12, 48, 64, 'Men\'s Athletic Fit Training Jersey', '2670573', 1, '119', '6741736ee37bd.png', 'The Men\'s Dri-FIT Training Jersey offers superior comfort and performance, featuring moisture-wicking technology and a lightweight design. Perfect for workouts or casual wear, this jersey keeps you cool and dry while providing a stylish athletic look.', '<p>The <strong>Men\'s Dri-FIT Training Jersey</strong> is crafted to support you through intense workouts and everyday activities. Made from high-quality, moisture-wicking Dri-FIT fabric, it efficiently pulls sweat away from your skin, keeping you dry and comfortable. The lightweight material and relaxed fit allow for a full range of motion, making it ideal for training, sports, or casual wear.</p>\r\n<p>This jersey features a classic crew neck and short sleeves, ensuring a timeless, versatile style. The breathable design enhances airflow, preventing overheating during high-intensity exercises. The bold Nike Swoosh logo on the chest adds a sporty touch, giving you that authentic athletic look.</p>\r\n<p>Available in various colors, the <strong>Men\'s Dri-FIT Training Jersey</strong> is the perfect combination of functionality and style, making it a must-have addition to any fitness wardrobe. Whether you\'re on the field, in the gym, or out with friends, this jersey delivers the comfort and performance you need.</p>', '999.99', '1499.99', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":144,\"name\":\"L\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":149,\"name\":\"Blue\",\"price\":35,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-24 05:55:46', NULL),
(22, 15, 12, 48, 60, 'Luxurious Soft Wool Blend Cardigan for Women with Cozy Comfort and Style', '5047069', 1, '125', '67415c3ff279f.png', 'This  Soft Wool Blend Cardigan offers a perfect mix of coziness and elegance. Crafted from a soft wool blend, it’s ideal for layering over any outfit to stay warm while looking stylish.', '<p>The <strong> Soft Wool Blend Cardigan</strong> is a must-have for any wardrobe, offering a cozy and sophisticated style that transitions beautifully from casual to more refined looks. Made from a soft wool blend, this cardigan provides warmth and comfort, while the elegant design ensures a flattering fit. The button-down closure, ribbed cuffs, and hem add a touch of structure, making it easy to style with various outfits.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re layering it over a simple t-shirt, pairing it with a dress, or using it as a chic topper for jeans and boots, this cardigan adds effortless style to any ensemble. The neutral color options make it versatile enough to pair with everything from workwear to weekend attire.</p>\r\n<p>Perfect for those chilly days or evenings, the Women\'s Soft Wool Blend Cardigan is an essential piece that combines practicality with timeless appeal.</p>', '145.99', '249.99', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":168,\"name\":\"L\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":100},\"Style\":{\"option_id\":173,\"name\":\"Layering\",\"price\":30,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-24 05:55:46', NULL),
(23, 16, 12, 48, 67, 'Men\'s Regular Fit Performance Sports Jersey for Active Wear and Everyday Comfort', '9716217', 1, '119', '674161f798422.png', 'The Men\'s Regular Fit Jersey offers the perfect balance of comfort and style. Made from soft, breathable fabric, it’s ideal for everyday wear, providing a relaxed fit and versatile look that pairs well with any casual outfit.', '<p>The <strong>Men\'s Regular Fit Jersey</strong> is designed for maximum comfort and effortless style. Made from high-quality cotton blend fabric, this jersey is soft to the touch and highly breathable, making it perfect for daily wear. The regular fit ensures a relaxed, non-restrictive feel that keeps you comfortable all day long, whether you’re running errands, lounging at home, or meeting friends.</p>\r\n<p>Featuring a simple crew neckline and short sleeves, this jersey offers a clean, minimalist look that easily complements any wardrobe. Available in a variety of classic colors, it’s easy to pair with jeans, shorts, or casual trousers for a laid-back, stylish outfit. The lightweight fabric also makes it ideal for layering or wearing on its own during warmer weather.</p>\r\n<p>Durable and versatile, the <strong>Men\'s Regular Fit Jersey</strong> is a wardrobe essential for men who value comfort and simplicity without compromising on style. Whether you’re relaxing or out on the go, this jersey will be a go-to for all your casual outfits.</p>', '11.75', '39.99', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":129,\"name\":\"L\",\"price\":2,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":134,\"name\":\"Red\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-24 05:57:43', NULL),
(24, 16, 12, 48, 62, 'Opulent Ivory Lace and Satin Bridal Gown with Exquisite Detailing and Timeless Elegance', '2614813', 1, '129', '67415d50b91c3.png', 'The Opulent Ivory Lace and Satin Bridal Gown is a breathtaking fusion of intricate lace details and smooth satin, designed to make every bride feel like royalty on her special day. With a flowing silhouette and elegant embellishments, this gown is the epitome of classic bridal beauty.', '<p>The <strong>Opulent Ivory Lace and Satin Bridal Gown</strong> is designed to capture the essence of elegance and sophistication. Made with luxurious lace and satin fabric, this gown features intricate lace detailing along the bodice, creating a delicate yet bold statement. The sweetheart neckline and sheer lace sleeves add a romantic, ethereal touch, while the voluminous satin skirt flows gracefully, offering a stunning silhouette that flatters every bride.</p>\r\n<p>The gown’s soft satin lining ensures comfort throughout the celebration, while the exquisite lace overlay adds an air of opulence. A dramatic train with lace accents enhances the gown’s refined look, making it perfect for walking down the aisle or posing for timeless wedding photos. The beautiful button-down back and subtle beading further elevate the dress, ensuring you shine on your special day.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you’re exchanging vows or dancing the night away, the <strong>Opulent Ivory Lace and Satin Bridal Gown</strong> will make you feel stunning and unforgettable, offering a perfect combination of tradition and modern bridal elegance.</p>', '499.99', '799.99', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":162,\"name\":\"L\",\"price\":50,\"stock\":100},\"Color Family\":{\"option_id\":167,\"name\":\"Black\",\"price\":100,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-24 05:57:43', NULL),
(25, 17, 13, 49, 94, 'Immersive VR Headset with 3D Audio and Motion Tracking', '4789486', 1, '137', '6742f62dbae48.png', 'Dive into virtual worlds with this immersive VR headset, featuring 3D audio, motion tracking, and crystal-clear visuals for a truly captivating experience.', '<p>Step into the future of gaming and entertainment with the Immersive VR Headset. Designed for an unparalleled experience, this headset offers stunning visuals with high-definition resolution, bringing virtual reality to life. The integrated 3D audio system enhances the experience, allowing you to hear every sound with incredible clarity and depth. Advanced motion tracking provides seamless interaction within your virtual environment, making your movements feel natural and fluid. Compatible with a variety of VR games and apps, this headset offers hours of fun and exploration in a comfortable, adjustable design. Whether you\'re gaming, exploring new worlds, or enjoying virtual media, this VR headset is your portal to endless possibilities.</p>', '299.99', '399.99', '{\"Features\":{\"option_id\":218,\"name\":\"Bluetooth VR Headset\",\"price\":50,\"stock\":100},\"Resolution\":{\"option_id\":221,\"name\":\"4K\",\"price\":40,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-25 06:41:07', NULL),
(26, 17, 13, 49, 92, 'Over-Ear Bluetooth Headphones with Noise Cancellation', '8793607', 1, '135', '6742f58782249.png', 'Enjoy superior sound and comfort with these over-ear Bluetooth headphones, featuring active noise cancellation, a long-lasting battery, and a comfortable fit for all-day wear.', '<p>Elevate your listening experience with the Over-Ear Bluetooth Headphones. Equipped with active noise cancellation, these headphones block out ambient noise, allowing you to immerse yourself fully in your music, podcasts, or calls. The cushioned ear cups ensure comfort during extended use, while the adjustable headband provides a perfect fit. Enjoy up to 20 hours of wireless playback on a single charge, with Bluetooth connectivity for seamless pairing with your devices. Whether you\'re traveling, working, or simply relaxing at home, these headphones deliver premium sound and noise isolation for an exceptional audio experience.</p>', '51.29', '129.99', '{\"Features\":{\"option_id\":223,\"name\":\"Over-Ear Noise\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":224,\"name\":\"Red\",\"price\":0,\"stock\":101}}', '2024-11-25 06:41:08', NULL),
(27, 17, 13, 49, 88, 'Nintendo Switch OLED Model with 64GB Storage', '8374782', 1, '139', '6742ee9920490.png', 'A versatile handheld and dockable gaming system featuring a 7-inch OLED display, 64GB storage, and enhanced audio for a premium gaming experience anywhere.', '<p>Experience gaming like never before with the Nintendo Switch OLED Model. The 7-inch OLED screen delivers vibrant colors and deep contrast, making your games come to life whether you’re playing at home or on the go. With 64GB of internal storage and the ability to expand via microSD, you have plenty of space for your favorite games and downloadable content. The enhanced audio provides immersive sound when handheld, while the updated kickstand offers multiple viewing angles for comfortable play. Dock it to your TV for a full console experience, and enjoy a vast library of games, from Mario to Zelda, in any setting.</p>', '269.49', '399.99', '{\"Color\":{\"option_id\":240,\"name\":\"White Joy-Con\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":100},\"Controller Type\":{\"option_id\":243,\"name\":\"Pro Controller Bundle\",\"price\":35,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-25 06:41:08', NULL);
