(39, 22, 14, 50, 107, 'Premium School Shoes – Comfortable, Durable, and Perfect for Everyday School Wear', '8947646', 1, '157', '674454650c803.png', 'Our Premium School Shoes combine durability, comfort, and style. Designed for active kids, these shoes offer all-day support, a sturdy build, and a polished look, making them perfect for school uniforms and daily wear.', '<p>Ensure your child steps into school with confidence and comfort with our <em>Premium School Shoes</em>! Crafted from high-quality materials, these shoes are designed to withstand the rigors of daily school life, providing long-lasting durability without compromising on style.</p>\r\n<p>The soft, cushioned insole and padded collar offer superior comfort, keeping little feet supported throughout the day. Breathable lining ensures proper ventilation, preventing moisture build-up and keeping feet fresh, even during long hours of wear.</p>\r\n<p>The sturdy, non-slip rubber sole provides excellent traction on various surfaces, ensuring safety during playtime and school activities. Reinforced stitching and a durable exterior make these shoes resistant to scuffs and everyday wear and tear, making them ideal for active children.</p>\r\n<p>Featuring a classic, polished design, these shoes are perfect for school uniforms, formal events, or casual wear. Easy-to-fasten options, such as Velcro straps or traditional laces, provide a secure fit and make them easy to put on and take off.</p>', '59.99', '89.99', NULL, '2024-11-26 06:28:36', NULL),
(40, 23, 14, 50, 118, 'Durable Kids\' Pencil Box – Stylish, Spacious, and Perfect for Organizing School Supplies', '8038712', 1, '155', '67445ecf3f8ed.png', 'Our Durable Kids\' Pencil Box is the perfect solution for keeping school supplies organized and easily accessible. With a spacious design, secure closure, and fun, colorful patterns, it’s ideal for pencils, erasers, and other school essentials.', '<p>Keep your child’s school supplies neatly organized with our <em>Durable Kids\' Pencil Box</em>! Designed to hold everything from pencils and pens to erasers and sharpeners, this pencil box is perfect for storing all their essentials in one place.</p>\r\n<p>Made from high-quality, sturdy materials, this pencil box features a secure snap closure to keep contents safe and prevent spills. Its compact size makes it easy to fit into school bags, desks, or lockers, while the vibrant colors and fun designs add a touch of personality to school accessories.</p>\r\n<p>The spacious interior provides plenty of room for all their writing instruments, while the simple, functional design ensures it’s easy for kids to use and keep tidy. Available in a variety of fun designs, including favorite characters and playful patterns, this pencil box will become your child’s go-to organizer.</p>\r\n<p>Whether for school, art projects, or everyday use, the <em>Durable Kids\' Pencil Box</em> is a must-have for young learners. Durable, practical, and fun, it’s the perfect addition to their school supplies collection!</p>', '9.99', '12.99', '{\"Color\":{\"option_id\":292,\"name\":\"Midnight Blue\",\"price\":2,\"stock\":100},\"Size\":{\"option_id\":295,\"name\":\"Jumbo\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-26 06:30:24', NULL),
(41, 23, 14, 50, 115, 'Kids\' Active Sportswear Set – Comfortable, Stylish, and Perfect for Every Adventure', '9792679', 1, '147', '67445da5c574c.png', 'Our Kids\' Active Sportswear Set is designed for active kids who love to play, run, and explore. Featuring breathable, stretchable fabrics and a stylish design, this set is perfect for sports, outdoor activities, and casual wear.', '<p>Get your little one ready for their next adventure with our <em>Kids\' Active Sportswear Set</em>! Whether it’s a day at the park, a soccer game, or simply running around with friends, this set offers the perfect combination of style, comfort, and performance.</p>\r\n<p>Crafted from breathable and moisture-wicking fabrics, this sportswear set ensures that your child stays cool and comfortable during even the most intense activities. The stretchable material provides flexibility and freedom of movement, making it ideal for sports like basketball, football, or running.</p>\r\n<p>The set includes a sporty T-shirt and matching shorts, both designed with vibrant colors and fun patterns that kids love. The elastic waistband ensures a snug fit, while the lightweight fabric offers durability and easy maintenance, even after countless washes.</p>\r\n<p>Available in a range of sizes and colors, the <em>Kids\' Active Sportswear Set</em> is perfect for every child who loves to stay active and stylish. Get ready for fun, play, and adventure, all while looking great in this comfortable and versatile sportswear set!</p>', '17.09', '55.99', '{\"Size\":{\"option_id\":300,\"name\":\"6Y\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100},\"Color\":{\"option_id\":303,\"name\":\"Pink\",\"price\":2,\"stock\":100}}', '2024-11-26 06:30:24', NULL),
