(105, 70, 10, 56, 20, 'Fresh Organic Broccoli – Nutritious, Crisp & Fresh Green', '2627639', 1, '87', '67359b8822084.png', 'Fresh, organic broccoli, packed with vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants. Ideal for steaming, roasting, or adding to salads and stir-fries, broccoli is a nutritious green vegetable that supports overall health and well-being.', '<p><strong>Fresh Organic Broccoli</strong> is a nutrient powerhouse that’s perfect for adding flavor, crunch, and color to your meals. With its rich green florets and hearty texture, broccoli is an essential vegetable in many dishes, from healthy salads to soups and stir-fries.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Fresh Organic Broccoli?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Packed with Nutrients:</strong> Broccoli is an excellent source of vitamin C, vitamin K, fiber, and folate. It also contains important minerals like potassium, calcium, and iron. The combination of these nutrients supports immune function, bone health, heart health, and overall vitality.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Antioxidant-Rich:</strong> Full of antioxidants, including sulforaphane and beta-carotene, broccoli helps to protect the body from oxidative stress and supports healthy aging. These antioxidants are essential for maintaining a strong immune system and fighting off inflammation.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Versatile &amp; Delicious:</strong> Whether you steam it, roast it with garlic and olive oil, add it to your stir-fries, or toss it into a fresh salad, broccoli is incredibly versatile. It’s also delicious when added to pasta dishes, casseroles, and even smoothies.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Supports a Healthy Lifestyle:</strong> Known for its cancer-fighting properties, broccoli is an excellent vegetable to include in a health-conscious diet. The high fiber content promotes digestive health, while its low calorie count makes it ideal for weight management.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Organic &amp; Fresh:</strong> Our broccoli is grown without pesticides or synthetic chemicals, ensuring a cleaner, healthier product for you and your family. Hand-harvested at its peak freshness, each bunch delivers the full range of benefits, both in taste and nutrition.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Add <strong>Fresh Organic Broccoli</strong> to your cart today and enjoy a nutritious, versatile, and delicious vegetable that will elevate your meals and support your health. Whether you’re looking to improve your diet or simply want a tasty addition to your plate, this broccoli will not disappoint.</p>\r\n<h4> </h4>', '3.14', '5.00', NULL, '2025-02-10 10:08:48', NULL),
(106, 70, 10, 56, 18, 'Fresh Cilantro – Organic, Fragrant, and Flavorful Herb', '7267795', 1, '87', '673599fc64f2a.png', 'Fresh cilantro (also known as coriander) is an aromatic herb that brings vibrant flavor to your dishes. Perfect for salads, salsas, garnishes, and cooked dishes, it’s a must-have for any kitchen. Packed with essential vitamins and antioxidants, cilantro adds both taste and nutrition to your meals.', '<p>Add a burst of fresh, aromatic flavor to your meals with our <strong>Fresh Organic Cilantro</strong>. Known for its fragrant leaves and bright green color, cilantro is an essential herb in many cuisines around the world. From Mexican tacos to Indian curries, cilantro offers a unique, fresh taste that elevates any dish.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Fresh Cilantro?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Rich in Nutrients:</strong> Cilantro is more than just a garnish—it’s packed with essential nutrients like vitamin A, vitamin K, and folate. It\'s also rich in antioxidants, which help protect your cells and support your overall health.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Versatile and Flavorful:</strong> Whether you\'re making a fresh salsa, tossing it into a salad, garnishing your favorite soup, or stirring it into a curry or stir-fry, cilantro adds a zesty, citrusy note that brightens up the flavor profile of any dish. Its fresh, fragrant leaves are perfect for adding a finishing touch to savory and even some sweet dishes.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Detoxifying Properties:</strong> Cilantro is known for its natural detoxifying properties. It’s been used for centuries to help remove heavy metals from the body and support healthy digestion. It’s a great addition to your diet for overall wellness.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>A Must-Have Kitchen Herb:</strong> Easy to grow, easy to use, and full of flavor, cilantro should be a staple in every kitchen. Whether you\'re a beginner home cook or a seasoned chef, this herb adds a fresh, natural zest to everything from salads to grilled meats to soups.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our <strong>Fresh Organic Cilantro</strong> is hand-picked to ensure top quality. No pesticides, no chemicals—just pure, organic freshness.</p>\r\n<p>Add a bunch to your cart today and enjoy the incredible flavors and benefits of this herb in your next meal!</p>\r\n<h4> </h4>', '1.85', '0.00', NULL, '2025-02-10 10:08:48', NULL),
(107, 70, 10, 56, 10, 'Juicy Cheeseburger – Tender, Savory, and Packed with Flavor', '1422037', 1, '81', '67347203a38a7.png', 'Our juicy cheeseburger is a perfect combination of a tender beef patty, melted cheese, and all the fresh toppings you love. Served on a soft, toasted bun, this burger is a deliciously satisfying meal for any time of the day.', '<p>Sink your teeth into the ultimate indulgence with our <strong>juicy cheeseburger</strong>. Made with a perfectly seasoned, tender beef patty, topped with melted cheese and fresh, crisp vegetables, this burger is a flavorful masterpiece that’s sure to satisfy your hunger.</p>\r\n<p>Our cheeseburgers are made with high-quality, fresh ingredients—premium beef, soft toasted buns, and rich, creamy cheese. Whether you\'re looking for a quick meal or a hearty treat, our cheeseburger offers the perfect balance of flavors and textures in every bite.</p>\r\n<p>Packed with savory goodness, our cheeseburger is not just a meal—it’s an experience. The juicy patty is complemented by melted cheese, fresh lettuce, tomatoes, onions, pickles, and a tangy sauce, all tucked into a perfectly toasted bun.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Cheeseburger?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Juicy &amp; Flavorful:</strong> A tender, perfectly seasoned beef patty with melted cheese and fresh toppings.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Made with Quality Ingredients:</strong> We use premium beef, fresh vegetables, and creamy cheese for a rich and satisfying burger.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Perfectly Toasted Bun:</strong> Each cheeseburger is served on a soft, warm, and toasted bun for added flavor and texture.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Savory Goodness in Every Bite:</strong> From the first bite to the last, every mouthful is a savory delight.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Perfectly Seasoned Beef Patty:</strong> Tender, juicy, and packed with flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Melted Cheese:</strong> Adds a creamy, savory richness to every bite.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fresh Toppings:</strong> Crisp lettuce, juicy tomatoes, onions, and pickles add the perfect crunch and freshness.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Premium Ingredients:</strong> Made with high-quality beef, cheese, and fresh vegetables for the ultimate cheeseburger experience.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Hearty &amp; Satisfying:</strong> A meal that will fill you up and leave you satisfied.</li>\r\n</ul>', '5.90', '0.00', NULL, '2025-02-10 10:08:48', NULL),
(108, 70, 10, 56, 11, 'Delicious Sandwich – Fresh, Tasty, and Perfect for Any Meal', '6968429', 1, '81', '673473298900d.png', 'Our delicious sandwich combines fresh ingredients, rich flavors, and a satisfying filling. Made with premium meats, fresh vegetables, and your favorite sauces, this sandwich is a convenient and tasty option for any meal, whether you’re on the go or relaxing at home.', '<p>Indulge in the goodness of our <strong>delicious sandwich</strong>, a perfect blend of fresh ingredients, satisfying fillings, and mouthwatering flavors. Made with premium ingredients, including high-quality meats, fresh veggies, and savory spreads, this sandwich is the ideal choice for a quick lunch, snack, or a hearty meal.</p>\r\n<p>Our sandwiches are crafted with care to offer a balanced combination of taste and nutrition. Whether you’re craving a classic deli-style sandwich or something with a little extra flair, we’ve got you covered. From grilled chicken to turkey, ham, or vegetarian options, our sandwiches are versatile and customizable to suit every taste.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Sandwich?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Fresh &amp; Tasty:</strong> Made with high-quality ingredients like tender meats, crisp veggies, and delicious spreads.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Perfectly Balanced:</strong> A satisfying filling that combines protein, fiber, and healthy fats for a delicious, well-rounded meal.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Customizable:</strong> Choose from a variety of fillings and sauces to suit your taste.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Quick &amp; Convenient:</strong> Ideal for lunch, a quick snack, or a meal on the go.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Fresh Ingredients:</strong> Only the freshest ingredients are used to ensure quality and flavor.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Premium Meats:</strong> Choose from a variety of high-quality deli meats like turkey, chicken, ham, or vegetarian options.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Crisp Fresh Veggies:</