(111, 71, 10, 46, 15, 'Pure Garlic Powder – Aromatic, Savory, and Perfect for Every Dish', '3202158', 1, '83', '67348013b5e8b.png', 'Elevate your cooking with our Pure Garlic Powder. This finely ground, aromatic powder is made from high-quality garlic and is perfect for seasoning meats, vegetables, sauces, soups, and more. Its savory, rich flavor will add depth to any dish you create.', '<p>Our <strong>Pure Garlic Powder</strong> is made from the finest garlic, carefully dried and ground to perfection to bring you the bold, savory taste of fresh garlic in an easy-to-use powder form. It’s the perfect way to add rich garlic flavor to your cooking without the hassle of peeling and chopping.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re preparing a hearty stew, a flavorful marinade, or just adding a savory kick to your vegetables, our garlic powder will enhance your meals with its aromatic, slightly sweet, and savory notes. It’s perfect for seasoning meats, soups, dressings, and dips, or simply sprinkling over roasted vegetables for that irresistible garlic flavor.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Garlic Powder?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>High-Quality Garlic:</strong> Made from premium garlic for a pure, authentic taste.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile &amp; Convenient:</strong> Perfect for a wide range of dishes, from meats to sauces, soups, and salads.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Rich, Savory Flavor:</strong> Adds a savory depth to any dish without the effort of chopping fresh garlic.</li>\r\n<li><strong>No Artificial Additives:</strong> Made without preservatives, fillers, or artificial colors—just pure, natural garlic flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Easy to Use:</strong> Finely ground for effortless incorporation into any dish.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Made from Premium Garlic:</strong> Sourced from the best garlic for an authentic and rich flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile Use:</strong> Ideal for seasoning meats, vegetables, soups, s