(131, 76, 15, 60, 135, 'Immersive VR Headset with 3D Audio and Motion Tracking', '2558355', 1, '173', '6746a42437d6c.png', 'Dive into virtual worlds with this immersive VR headset, featuring 3D audio, motion tracking, and crystal-clear visuals for a truly captivating experience.', '<div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-description\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"content mb-30 summernote-content\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-description\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"content mb-30 summernote-content\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-description\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"content mb-30 summernote-content\">\r\n<p>Step into the future of gaming and entertainment with the Immersive VR Headset. Designed for an unparalleled experience, this headset offers stunning visuals with high-definition resolution, bringing virtual reality to life. The integrated 3D audio system enhances the experience, allowing you to hear every sound with incredible clarity and depth. Advanced motion tracking provides seamless interaction within your virtual environment, making your movements feel natural and fluid. Compatible with a variety of VR games and apps, this headset offers hours of fun and exploration in a comfortable, adjustable design. Whether you\'re gaming, exploring new worlds, or enjoying virtual media, this VR headset is your portal to endless possibilities.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '299.99', '399.99', '{\"Features\":{\"variation_id\":172,\"option_id\":406,\"name\":\"Bluetooth VR Headset\",\"price\":54,\"stock\":11},\"Resolution\":{\"variation_id\":173,\"option_id\":409,\"name\":\"