(137, 78, 15, 60, 143, 'TechVision AirPro 13-Inch Ultra-Slim Lightweight Laptop with Retina Display', '9077573', 1, '177', '6746cfeba01b1.png', 'The TechVision AirPro 13-Inch Ultra-Slim Laptop offers the perfect blend of performance and portability. Featuring a stunning Retina display, powerful processor, and lightweight design, it’s ideal for professionals, students, and creators on the go.', '<p>Unleash your productivity with the TechVision AirPro 13-Inch Ultra-Slim Laptop. Designed for ultimate efficiency, it boasts a vibrant Retina display with razor-sharp resolution, bringing your content to life with stunning clarity and color accuracy. Powered by an advanced processor and 8GB of RAM, it delivers smooth multitasking, whether you’re working, streaming, or creating.</p>\r\n<p>The sleek aluminum body is not only stylish but also incredibly lightweight, making it easy to carry wherever you go. With an all-day battery life, you can stay connected and productive without constantly searching for an outlet. The advanced SSD storage ensures lightning-fast boot times and file access.</p>\r\n<p>Perfect for those who demand performance and style, the TechVision AirPro redefines what a portable laptop can be. Elevate your experience and stay ahead of the curve!</p>', '999.99', '1299.99', '{\"Audio Technology\":{\"variation_id\":184,\"option_id\":430,\"name\":\"Dolby Audio\",\"price\":75,\"stock\":99},\"Color\":{\"variation_id\":185,\"option_id\":433,\"name\":\"Metallic Silver\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":99}}', '2025-02-20 13:48:44', NULL),
(138, 78, 15, 60, 137, '55\" 4K Smart LED TV with HDR and Voice Control', '6144220', 1, '177', '6746a67fda5c9.png', 'A sleek 55\" 4K Smart LED TV featuring HDR technology and voice control. Enjoy stunning visuals, smart apps, and seamless streaming for an ultimate viewing experience.', '<div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-description\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"content mb-30 summernote-content\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade active show\">\r\n<div class=\"tab-description\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n<div class=\"content mb-30 summernote-content\">\r\n<p>Experience true-to-life picture quality with the 55\" 4K Smart LED TV. Equipped with HDR technology, this TV delivers stunning contrast, vivid colors, and sharp detail, bringing your favorite movies and shows to life. The built-in smart platform gives you access to popular streaming apps like Netflix, YouTube, and Prime Video. Integrated voice control lets you navigate effortlessly, while multiple HDMI and USB ports ensure easy connectivity with other devices. Its slim, modern design enhances any living space, providing both elegance and entertainment. Perfect for families, gamers, and movie enthusiasts.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '399.99', '599.99', '{\"Color\":{\"variation_id\":168,\"option_id\":399,\"name\":\"Metallic Silver\",\"price\":15,\"stock\":100},\"Audio Technology\":{\"variation_id\":169,\"option_id\":401,\"name\":\"Dolby Atmos\",\"price\":100,\"stock\":99}}', '2025-02-20 13:48:44', NULL),
(139, 79, 12, 48, 50, 'Ready Boy\'s Stylish Cotton Outfit Set for Comfort and Everyday Adventure', '3247955', 1, '117', '674155f7ae2fa.png', 'Let your little explorer roam in comfort and style with our Ready Boy’s Cotton Outfit Set. Durable, soft, and designed for active play, this set is perfect for everyday adventures and special outings.', '<p>Gear up your young adventurer with our Adventure-Ready Boy’s Cotton Outfit Set. Crafted from high-quality, breathable cotton, this outfit ensures all-day comfort, whether he’s at school, on the playground, or at a family outing. The soft, lightweight fabric allows for easy movement, keeping him cool and comfortable during all his activities.</p>\r\n<p>Designed with fun and functionality in mind, this set features a stylish t-shirt with eye-catching prints and a pair of durable shorts or pants with an elastic waistband for a secure fit. The reinforced seams and sturdy materials stand up to rough-and-tumble play, ensuring the outfit remains in great shape wash after wash.</p>\r\n<p>Available in a variety of colors and patterns, this versatile set makes mixing and matching easy. It’s perfect for everything from casual playdates to birthday parties. Give your little one the confidence to take on the world with comfort, style, and durability he can count on.</p>', '22.99', '34.99', '{\"Color Family\":{\"variation_id\":73,\"option_id\":198,\"name\":\"Red\",\"price\":2,\"stock\":100},\"Size\":{\"variation_id\":74,\"option_id\":203,\"name\":\"Large\",\"price\":10,\"stock\":100}}', '2025-02-23 05:15:16', NULL),
