(141, 79, 12, 48, 47, 'Classic Cotton Crewneck Shirt with Timeless Style and Everyday Comfort', '2896925', 1, '113', '674153bcadf72.png', 'Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style with our Classic Cotton Crewneck T-Shirt. Designed for versatility, this essential tee offers a modern fit and timeless appeal, making it a go-to choice for any occasion. Whether you\'re dressing up for a night out or relaxing on the weekend, this t-shirt ensures you stay effortlessly stylish and comfortable throughout the day.', '<p>Upgrade your everyday wardrobe with the Classic Cotton Crewneck T-Shirt, meticulously crafted from high-quality, breathable cotton. This soft, durable fabric provides all-day comfort while maintaining its shape and texture, even after multiple washes. The crewneck design offers a classic, clean-cut look that complements any outfit, making it easy to dress up or down.</p>\r\n<p>Perfect for layering or wearing on its own, this t-shirt is a versatile staple that pairs well with jeans, chinos, or shorts. Its modern fit strikes the right balance between relaxed and tailored, ensuring a flattering silhouette for all body types. Available in a wide range of colors, this tee is ideal for mixing and matching, allowing you to express your personal style effortlessly.</p>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re heading to work, hanging out with friends, or enjoying a quiet day at home, the Classic Cotton Crewneck T-Shirt is your reliable choice for comfort and style. Experience the quality craftsmanship and timeless design that make this tee a must-have addition to any wardrobe.</p>', '19.99', '29.99', '{\"Size\":{\"variation_id\":39,\"option_id\":96,\"name\":\"L\",\"price\":3,\"stock\":100},\"Color Family\":{\"variation_id\":40,\"option_id\":101,\"name\":\"Blue\",\"price\":5,\"stock\":100}}', '2025-02-23 05:15:16', NULL),
(145, 81, 14, 59, 101, 'Art & Craft Kits – Creative Fun for All Ages', '6563963', 1, '149', '674442abb6d41.png', 'Unleash your creativity with our Art & Craft Kits! Perfect for kids, beginners, or seasoned artists, these kits provide everything you need to craft beautiful, personalized projects and explore your artistic talents.', '<p>Dive into the world of creativity with our <em>Art &amp; Craft Kits</em>! Whether you\'re a budding artist or just looking for a fun, hands-on activity, these all-in-one kits are designed to inspire and engage. Packed with high-quality materials, each kit comes with everything you need to create stunning works of art—from paints and brushes to paper, beads, and more.</p>\r\n<p>Our kits are perfect for kids, teens, and adults alike, offering a variety of craft activities such as painting, drawing, jewelry-making, scrapbooking, and more. Each kit is carefully curated to ensure ease of use, with step-by-step instructions to guide you through each project.</p>\r\n<p>Not only are these Art &amp; Craft Kits an ideal way to spend quality time with family and friends, but they also promote essential skills like fine motor development, creativity, and problem-solving. These kits make excellent gifts for birthdays, holidays, or any occasion that calls for a creative touch.</p>\r\n<p>With a wide range of themes and projects, including seasonal crafts, DIY decorations, and personalized gift ideas, there’s a kit to suit every taste and occasion. Let your imagination run wild and create beautiful, one-of-a-kind pieces with our Art &amp; Craft Kits!</p>', '19.99', '24.99', '[]', '2025-02-25 04:43:30', NULL),
(146, 81, 14, 59, 104, 'School Backpack – Durable, Spacious, and Comfortable for Kids', '2809861', 1, '153', '674444aa7fa2f.png', 'Our Premium School Backpack is designed to meet the needs of active kids. With spacious compartments, padded straps, and durable materials, it’s the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality for school and everyday use.', '<p>Prepare your child for the school year with our <em>Premium School Backpack</em>! Built to withstand the rigors of daily use, this backpack combines style, durability, and comfort in one. Made from high-quality, water-resistant materials, it’s designed to keep books, notebooks, and school supplies safe and organized.</p>\r\n<p>Featuring a spacious main compartment and additional pockets for smaller items, this backpack has plenty of room for everything your child needs for a day at school. From textbooks and stationery to lunch boxes and water bottles, everything has its place. The easy-to-access front pocket is perfect for storing pens, keys, or even a phone.</p>\r\n<p>Comfort is key with this backpack’s padded shoulder straps, which provide extra support and reduce pressure, making it easy for your child to carry their essentials without strain. The breathable back panel ensures airflow to keep your child comfortable, even during long days.</p>\r\n<p>With a fun, vibrant design, this backpack is sure to brighten up your child\'s school day. Whether they\'re in elementary school or high school, this versatile backpack is an ideal choice for students of all ages. Available in multiple colors and patterns, there\'s a style to suit every personality.</p>', '52.79', '89.99', '{\"Color\":{\"variation_id\":148,\"option_id\":356,\"name\":\"Navy Blue\",\"price\":\"10.00\",\"stock\":100},\"Size\":{\"variation_id\":149,\"option_id\":359,\"name\":\"Medium\",\"price\":\"20.00\",\"stock\":100}}', '2025-02-25 04:43:30', NULL),
(184, 112, 15, 51, 143, 'TechVision AirPro 13-Inch Ultra-Slim Lightweight Laptop with Retina Display', '9077573', 1, '177', '6746cfeba01b1.png', 'The TechVision AirPro 13-Inch Ultra-Slim Laptop offers the perfect blend of performance and portability. Featuring a stunning Retina display, powerful processor, and lightweight design, it’s ideal for professionals, students, and creators on the go.', '<p>Unleash your productivity with the TechVision AirPro 13-Inch Ultra-Slim Laptop. Designed for ultimate efficiency, it boasts a vibrant Retina display with razor-sharp resolution, bringing your content to life with stunning clarity and color accuracy. Powered by an advanced processor and 8GB of RAM, it delivers smooth multitasking, whether you’re working, streaming, or creating.</p>\r\n<p>The sleek aluminum body is not only stylish but also incredibly lightweight, making it easy to carry wherever you go. With an all-day battery life, you can stay connected and productive without constantly searching for an outlet. The advanced SSD storage ensures lightning-fast boot times and file access.</p>\r\n<p>Perfect for those who demand performance and style, the TechVision AirPro redefines what a portable laptop can be. Elevate your experience and stay ahead of the curve!</p>', '999.99', '1299.99', '{\"Audio Technology\":{\"variation_id\":184,\"option_id\":430,\"name\":\"Dolby Audio\",\"price\":\"75.00\",\"stock\":98},\"Color\":{\"variation_id\":185,\"option_id\":433,\"name\":\"Metallic Silver\",\"price\":\"10.00\",\"stock\":98}}', '2025-03-05 09:57:35', NULL),
(210, 132, 12, 48, 67, 'Men\'s Regular Fit Performance Sports Jersey for Active Wear and Everyday Comfort', '9716217', 1, '119', '674161f798422.png', 'The Men\'s Regular Fit Jersey offers the perfect balance of comfort and style. Made from soft, breathable fabric, it’s ideal for everyday wear, providing a relaxed fit and versatile look that pairs well with any casual outfit.', '<p>The <strong>Men\'s Regular Fit Jersey</strong> is designed for maximum comfort and effortless style. Made from high-quality cotton blend fabric, this jersey is soft to the touch and highly breathable, making it perfect for daily wear. The regular fit ensures a relaxed, non-restrictive feel that keeps you comfortable all day long, whether you’re running errands, lounging at home, or meeting friends.</p>\r\n<p>Featuring a simple crew neckline and short sleeves, this jersey offers a clean, minimalist look that easily complements any wardrobe. Available in a variety of classic colors, it’s easy to pair with jeans, shorts, or casual trousers for a laid-back, stylish outfit. The lightweight fabric also makes it ideal for layering or wearing on its own during warmer weather.</p>\r\n<p>Durable and versatile, the <strong>Men\'s Regular Fit Jersey</strong> is a wardrobe essential for men who value comfort and simplicity without compromising on style. Whether you’re relaxing or out on the go, this jersey will be a go-to for all your casual outfits.</p>', '11.75', '39.99', '{\"Size\":{\"variation_id\":50,\"option_id\":131,\"name\":\"XXL\",\"price\":\"5.00\",\"stock\":99},\"Color\":{\"variation_id\":51,\"option_id\":132,\"name\":\"Black\",\"price\":\"2.00\",\"stock\":100}}', '2025-03-08 08:24:26', NULL),
(231, 150, 10, 46, 17, 'Fresh Organic Spinach – Nutrient-Rich & Healthy Green', '2757442', 1, '87', '67359938d03f9.png', 'Experience the fresh, vibrant taste of organic spinach—packed with vitamins, antioxidants, and essential minerals. Ideal for everything from fresh salads to smoothies and cooked dishes, our spinach is your go-to green for a healthy, balanced lifestyle.', '<p><strong>Fresh Organic Spinach</strong> is a versatile, nutrient-packed powerhouse that should be a staple in every kitchen. Grown organically with care, this leafy green brings a fresh, crisp flavor to any dish, while offering a host of health benefits. Whether you’re blending it into a smoothie, tossing it into a salad, or sautéing it in a stir-fry, spinach enhances the taste and nutrition of any meal.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Fresh Spinach?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Loaded with Nutrients:</strong> Our spinach is an excellent source of vitamin A, vitamin C, and vitamin K, along with essential minerals like iron, magnesium, and calcium. These vitamins and minerals support everything from bone health to immune function and skin vitality.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Powerful Antioxidants:</strong> Spinach is a rich source of antioxidants, including flavonoids and carotenoids, which help protect the body against oxidative stress and promote healthy aging. The high fiber content also aids digestion and supports a healthy gut.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Versatility in the Kitchen:</strong> Spinach is one of the most versatile greens. You can use it fresh in salads, blend it into nutrient-packed smoothies, add it to your favorite pasta dishes, soups, or enjoy it sautéed with garlic and olive oil. The possibilities are endless.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Perfect for Your Wellness Journey:</strong> Low in calories and high in essential nutrients, spinach is perfect for weight management and general well-being. It helps with detoxification, promotes healthy digestion, and strengthens the immune system.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Whether you\'re a health-conscious individual looking to improve your diet, a busy professional in need of a quick and nutritious meal, or someone who simply loves fresh, organic greens, our <strong>Fresh Organic Spinach</strong> is the perfect addition to your cart.</p>\r\n<p>Buy a bunch today and enjoy the crisp, fresh taste that only organic spinach can offer—your body will thank you!</p>\r\n<h4> </h4>', '2.99', '0.00', NULL, '2025-03-09 05:21:31', NULL),
(232, 150, 10, 46, 18, 'Fresh Cilantro – Organic, Fragrant, and Flavorful Herb', '7267795', 1, '87', '673599fc64f2a.png', 'Fresh cilantro (also known as coriander) is an aromatic herb that brings vibrant flavor to your dishes. Perfect for salads, salsas, garnishes, and cooked dishes, it’s a must-have for any kitchen. Packed with essential vitamins and antioxidants, cilantro adds both taste and nutrition to your meals.', '<p>Add a burst of fresh, aromatic flavor to your meals with our <strong>Fresh Organic Cilantro</strong>. Known for its fragrant leaves and bright green color, cilantro is an essential herb in many cuisines around the world. From Mexican tacos to Indian curries, cilantro offers a unique, fresh taste that elevates any dish.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Fresh Cilantro?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Rich in Nutrients:</strong> Cilantro is more than just a garnish—it’s packed with essential nutrients like vitamin A, vitamin K, and folate. It\'s also rich in antioxidants, which help protect your cells and support your overall health.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Versatile and Flavorful:</strong> Whether you\'re making a fresh salsa, tossing it into a salad, garnishing your favorite soup, or stirring it into a curry or stir-fry, cilantro adds a zesty, citrusy note that brightens up the flavor profile of any dish. Its fresh, fragrant leaves are perfect for adding a finishing touch to savory and even some sweet dishes.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>Detoxifying Properties:</strong> Cilantro is known for its natural detoxifying properties. It’s been used for centuries to help remove heavy metals from the body and support healthy digestion. It’s a great addition to your diet for overall wellness.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><strong>A Must-Have Kitchen Herb:</strong> Easy to grow, easy to use, and full of flavor, cilantro should be a staple in every kitchen. Whether you\'re a beginner home cook or a seasoned chef, this herb adds a fresh, natural zest to everything from salads to grilled meats to soups.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Our <strong>Fresh Organic Cilantro</strong> is hand-picked to ensure top quality. No pesticides, no chemicals—just pure, organic freshness.</p>\r\n<p>Add a bunch to your cart today and enjoy the incredible flavors and benefits of this herb in your next meal!</p>\r\n<h4> </h4>', '1.85', '0.00', NULL, '2025-03-09 05:21:31', NULL),
(233, 150, 10, 46, 10, 'Juicy Cheeseburger – Tender, Savory, and Packed with Flavor', '1422037', 1, '81', '67347203a38a7.png', 'Our juicy cheeseburger is a perfect combination of a tender beef patty, melted cheese, and all the fresh toppings you love. Served on a soft, toasted bun, this burger is a deliciously satisfying meal for any time of the day.', '<p>Sink your teeth into the ultimate indulgence with our <strong>juicy cheeseburger</strong>. Made with a perfectly seasoned, tender beef patty, topped with melted cheese and fresh, crisp vegetables, this burger is a flavorful masterpiece that’s sure to satisfy your hunger.</p>\r\n<p>Our cheeseburgers are made with high-quality, fresh ingredients—premium beef, soft toasted buns, and rich, creamy cheese. Whether you\'re looking for a quick meal or a hearty treat, our cheeseburger offers the perfect balance of flavors and textures in every bite.</p>\r\n<p>Packed with savory goodness, our cheeseburger is not just a meal—it’s an experience. The juicy patty is complemented by melted cheese, fresh lettuce, tomatoes, onions, pickles, and a tangy sauce, all tucked into a perfectly toasted bun.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Why Choose Our Cheeseburger?</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Juicy &amp; Flavorful:</strong> A tender, perfectly seasoned beef patty with melted cheese and fresh toppings.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Made with Quality Ingredients:</strong> We use premium beef, fresh vegetables, and creamy cheese for a rich and satisfying burger.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Perfectly Toasted Bun:</strong> Each cheeseburger is served on a soft, warm, and toasted bun for added flavor and texture.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Savory Goodness in Every Bite:</strong> From the first bite to the last, every mouthful is a savory delight.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>Key Features:</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Perfectly Seasoned Beef Patty:</strong> Tender, juicy, and packed with flavor.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Melted Cheese:</strong> Adds a creamy, savory richnes